text: Sven Montan (22 July 1887 - 29 May 1971) was a Swedish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
